---
title: Application Craft on the Chrome Web Store
class_name: cws
full_width: true
---

<header>
  <div class="container">
    <div>
      <h1>Chrome Web Store</h1>
      <h2>The Full Application Craft Experience via the Chrome Web Store</h2>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>


<div class="container">

  <div id="chrome-signup" class="clearfix">
    <section>
      <script src="http://ac-static.applicationcraft.com/ac/1.20/live/userlive.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
      <script type="text/javascript">
        waInitForm("a286024b-a0ca-4107-8f4c-5a8f1e32cefe", '100%', 600, { referrer: document.referrer }, null, null, "http://ac.applicationcraft.com/live.html");
      </script>
    </section>

    <section>
      <%= image_tag 'ac-site-cws-logo.png' %>

      <h2>Start your journey here...</h2>
      <p>Just complete this short form to start your free trial, then the next time you visit this page via Chrome, you will signed straight into your new AC account.</p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div id="chrome-signin" class="clearfix">
    <%= image_tag 'ac-site-cws-logo.png' %>
    <div>
      <h2>Your journey continues...</h2>
      <p>Looks like you've already signed up. That's fantastic! Wait just a few seconds while we redirect you to your account...</p>
      <p>If you are still waiting after 10 seconds, please <a href="#">click here</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="chrome-signin-list" class="clearfix">
    <%= image_tag 'ac-site-cws-logo.png' %>
    <div>
      <h2>Your journey continues...</h2>
      <p>Looks like you've already signed up for a few accounts. That's fantastic! Please select which account you would like to sign in to...</p>
      <ul></ul>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<% content_for :foot do %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'cws' %>
<% end %>
